https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=44424	45931
<div align="center"><a href="https://twitter.com/TMCorp/status/609167065300271104"><img src="http://img.solidot.com.cn/0/792/liQIAVgxVaq32.png" align=""></a><br>
<br>
</div>
